<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Good morning, <PARENT>. I'm so tired...
How do you always get up so early?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Good morning, <PARENT>. You'll be working
in the farm again today? I'll help you,
if I can!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Good morning, <PARENT>. Our farm is so
much bigger than other people's houses.
All my friends are so jealous!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>, <PARENT>. Could I bring a friend
over to the house one day soon? Go on,
say it's okay!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I wonder if one of my friends would like
to come over. We can play house! You can
play too, <PARENT>.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>, did you like playing house? I
really love it! I'm always the mom.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<PARENT>, welcome home. I'm tired! Please
pick me up...

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>, welcome home. I've been helping
out on the farm! I have!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>, welcome home! Will you read me
a book tonight? Please?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>, it's all sparkly outside. How
beautiful!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
It's raining today. I bet the plants
are loving it!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>, I want to something to drink!
Please, give me something.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Tell me, <PARENT>. Why are the rain drops
bigger in summer? I want to know!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Hey, <PARENT>. Will you play with me
today?
<PAGE>
Look how great the weather is! Come on,
play with me, <PARENT>!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
It's raining. I need to be careful not
to get my skirt dirty.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>! Let's play in the snow! Come on,
quick, quick!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Hey, <PARENT>. I wish it would snow a
little more, don't you? I'm going to
make a big igloo tomorrow!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<PARENT>, I'm scared of the wind! Don't
leave me alone, okay? Promise?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>, look at that snow storm! If it
stops by tomorrow can I go out and play?
I won't do anything dangerous!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I often play explorer here. It's a
lot of fun, pretending to discover
things!
<PAGE>
<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>I found this mushroom that lets you jump
really high if you climb on top of it.
Bouncing around is such fun!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
There are lots of animals here, too.
They pop their little faces out as you
walk by. We're all friends!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I often play explorer here. It's a
lot of fun, pretending to discover
things!
<PAGE>
If you fall into the river you get
something sparkly. Did you know that?
I've been collecting them!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
You can see loads of fish here. I saw
a big fish jumping out the water the
other day! I was really surprised!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I often play explorer here. It's a
lot of fun, pretending to discover
things!
<PAGE>
<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>I met this funny lady by the lake. When
I asked her how old she was she got a
bit upset.
<PAGE>
<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>"It's most impolite to ask a Goddess
her age!" That's what she said to me. I
bet she's really old, but she was nice.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
This place is so high up. If you look
down from above all the people look so
small!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>, can I help you with anything?
I can do whatever you need!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>. Over here! Come on, let's play.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Uh, I don't like this place. <PARENT>,
make sure you don't leave me in here!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
What? We aren't leaving yet? Let's get
out of here, <PARENT>!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>, why aren't there more people
here in town? Why don't more people move
here?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Who should I play with today? Who do
you think, <PARENT>?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Who should I play with today? Who do
you think, <PARENT>?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Who should I play with today? Who do
you think, <PARENT>?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
You always look so busy, <PARENT>. Please
play with me sometimes?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I love exploring the town. I'm going to
find buried treasure one day, I know it!
<PAGE>
<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>When I do, I'll show it to you first.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
<PARENT>, your job is really interesting.
Helping you out is so exciting.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Dunhill is really interesting, isn't he?
He tells me so many stories about this
town!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
When I'm all grown up I want to do work
that will challenge me. Do you think
I'm going to grow up soon?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Tell me, <PARENT>. Was I cute when I was a
baby?
<PAGE>
<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>R-Really? Heh heh...

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Tell me, <PARENT>. Tell me all about
farming. Once I grow up I'm going to be
a farmer too.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>'s pancakes! Your cooking is
the best, <PARENT>!
<PAGE>
Time to dig in! Wow, they're great!
Thank you, <PARENT>!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Thank you, <PARENT>! Wow, this looks
delicious!
<PAGE>
Time to dig in! Oh, delicious!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Great! I'm going to show this to
everyone.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Thank you, <PARENT>! You're present made
me really happy.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<PARENT>... I don't want this. O-Okay,
okay! I'll take it, just don't get any
angrier!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
Ugh, grilled pumpkin? This is the thing
I hate most of the most! <PARENT>!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
It's a big watermelon! Wow, thanks
<PARENT>! Let's all eat it together.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Wow! I don't think I've ever seen such
a big one before! I've got to show this
to my friends.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Whoa! Amazing! That's one huge
watermelon. Did you grow it, <PARENT>?
<PAGE>
You're amazing, <PARENT>. Let's all eat it
together.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Wow! I don't think I've ever seen such

to my friends.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Sorry, I don't really want this.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
I don't need anything else today. Sorry,
<PARENT>.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>

Great! What did you get me?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
I fell asleep on the farm and woke up
to find this chick bouncing on my head!
So very cute!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
This chicken can make a lot of noise.
It always wakes me up in the morning!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
It's so big... And looks strong, too. I
think I've found my bodyguard.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
I always play with this dog. Everyone in
town is jealous!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
I think our dog is getting a bit fat.
Definitely fatter than before, right?
I can hardly move the poor thing around!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Our dog is so big. I love to ride around
on its big, broad back! So fast, too!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Who... who's dog is this? What? Our dog?
I couldn't tell, with all that fat!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Our cat sometimes comes into my bed. So
fluffy and warm!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Our cat sometimes comes into my bed. I
can never sleep with this fat fluff ball
sitting on me!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Carrying our cat around is lovely. So
warm and fluffy.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
So heavy! You're really strong, <PARENT>,
being able to carry such a beast around
with you!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Thank you, <PARENT>. The flowers are
beautiful.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Great! Pumpkin Festival candy! Thank
you, <PARENT>.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
What a beautiful feather. I want one
too! What? I can't have one?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Wow, a ring! It's so nice. I want one
too. Can I have one?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
I was feeding them in the forest and
lots of their little friends showed up.
It's a lot of fun playing with animals!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
They always come to say hello when I go
into the forest. They're my friends.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Hee hee hee. Look at that face! How
lovely!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>, here you are! Your birthday
present from me. I hope you like it...

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<PARENT>. I'm sorry. It's your birthday...
and I forgot...

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
<PARENT>... don't you like me any more?
Let's talk, please...

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Wow! It's the sea! Amazing, look how big
it is!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Hey, look at that turtle. Do you think I
could ride it?
<PAGE>
<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>Ah hah hah, no need to panic <PARENT>!
Don't worry, I won't do anything
dangerous.

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
<PARENT>! I want to eat some coconut!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Hey... what's with this place? It's a
little scary...
<PAGE>
There aren't any... ghosts here, are
there? Whoa! I'm just... just imagining
things, right?

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Hey, I just saw a monkey! It was all
golden and yellow, and it ran off when
it saw me!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
There's something weird hanging on the
wall over there!
<PAGE>
<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>Whoa! A scary mask!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Wow! What a wonderful garden!
<PAGE>
Look at all the flowers!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_NORMAL>
Do you think there are lots of fish in
that pond?
<PAGE>
<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>Hey, don't even think about fishing!
Play with me for a while, come on!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
I don't need any of that horrible,
bitter green tea. Ugh!
<PAGE>
<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>But I'll have some more of those tasty
treats!<RED>∀</RED>

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ROUGH>
Snow, snow, lovely snow! 
<PAGE>
Hey, <PARENT>! Let's make a big snowman!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>
Whoa! It's slippery...
<PAGE>
<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>That surprised me. I almost fell over!

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Atchoo!
<PAGE>
<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_ANGRY>That wasn't a sneeze! Don't worry about
me. We're not leaving yet! Come on, I
want to play more!

...<PARENT>, let's play. I want to play
some more...

<FACE_CHILD_G><POS_RIGHT><FACE_SAD>
Ugh, I feel horrible... so hot...!
Now's not the time for presents.
